{
  "uid": "aegisml-obs",
  "title": "AegisML — HTTP & deployment (baseline)",
  "tags": ["aegisml", "prometheus"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": { "selected": true, "text": "Prometheus", "value": "Prometheus" },
        "hide": 0
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Request volume",
      "description": "Total HTTP request rate across all routes (excludes scrape of /metrics).",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(aegisml_http_requests_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "req/s"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10 } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Latency (p95)",
      "description": "End-to-end HTTP handler time (middleware), 95th percentile.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(aegisml_http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p95"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "s", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10 } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "5xx share of traffic",
      "description": "Fraction of responses with HTTP 5xx status (from request counter).",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(aegisml_http_requests_total{status=~\"5..\"}[5m])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(aegisml_http_requests_total[5m])), 1e-9)",
          "legendFormat": "5xx_ratio"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "percentunit", "min": 0, "max": 1, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 15 } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "HTTP error events / s (4xx vs 5xx)",
      "description": "Low-cardinality error counter from middleware (`aegisml_http_errors_total`).",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(aegisml_http_errors_total[5m])) by (class)",
          "legendFormat": "{{class}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 12 } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Deployment metadata (`aegisml_app_info`)",
      "description": "Labels: service, version, environment, git_commit, pod, namespace. One row per scraped target/replica.",
      "type": "table",
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "aegisml_app_info",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "custom": { "align": "auto", "inspect": false } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "showHeader": true }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Process start (Unix time)",
      "description": "When this replica registered metrics — compare across pods during rollouts.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 16 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "aegisml_process_start_timestamp_seconds",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "none", "decimals": 0, "custom": { "align": "auto" } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "value" }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Notes",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 25 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Day-1 checks:** rising **5xx share** or **5xx events/s** → logs for that pod (`git_commit` / `pod_name` must match **`aegisml_app_info`**). **p95 latency** jump after **process start** → regression or load.\n\n**Identity:** HTTP series are not version-labeled (cardinality); use **`aegisml_app_info`** + structured logs for release correlation."
      }
    }
  ]
}
